{"word":"H1310 - בָּשַׁל - bâshal - baw-shal' - Bake - சுடு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>בָּשַׁל"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâshal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-shal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bake / சுடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சமை, அவிக்கப்படு, சமைக்கப்படு, முதிர், வேலி, பொரி, அவி, பொங்கு, சுடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to boil, to cook, to bake, to roast, to ripen, to grow ripe"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to boil, to cook"},{"paragraph":"2) to grow ripe, to ripen"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to boil"},{"paragraph":"2) to cook"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be boiled"},{"paragraph":"2) to be sodden"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to ripen"},{"paragraph":"2) to ripen, to be brought to ripeness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>boil</i> up; hence to <i>be done</i> in cooking; figuratively to <i>ripen: - </i>bake, boil, bring forth, is ripe, roast, seethe, sod (be sodden)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1310 - בָּשַׁל - bâshal - baw-shal'/1310\">H1310</a>, <a href=\"#/H1311 - בָּשֵׁל - bâshêl - baw-shale'/1311\">H1311</a>, <a href=\"#/H1312 - בִּשְׁלָם - Bishlâm - bish-lawm'/1312\">H1312</a>, <a href=\"#/H4018 - מְבַשְּׁלָה - mᵉbashshᵉlâh - meb-ash-shel-aw'/4018\">H4018</a>"}]}